   "source": [
    "# District heating areas in Denmark\n",
    "\n",
    "```{post} 2023-04-14\n",
    ":tags: open science\n",
    ":author: Adam R. Jensen\n",
    ":image: 2\n",
    "```\n",
    "\n",
    "This blog posts demonstrates how to generate a map of the district heating areas in Denmark. Pretty expansive coverage don't ya think?\n",
    "\n",
    "Vector data of the district heating areas can be obtained from [PlanData.dk](https://kort.plandata.dk). To download the district heating area shapefiles, select \"Værktøjer\" then click \"Download tema\" and tick the box \"Forsyningsområde, vedtaget\"."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 1,
   "id": "6d6f6a6d-f28a-45a6-ae7e-022761fe6e67",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
    "import matplotlib.patches as mpatches\n",
    "import geopandas as gpd\n",
    "import cartopy\n",
    "import cartopy.crs as ccrs\n",
    "import cartopy.feature as cfeature\n",
    "import os"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 2,
   "id": "f167521a-45be-4149-b9d3-0f72403a92a1",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Read data using geopandas\n",
    "df_dh = gpd.read_file(\"../data/danish_district_heating_areas.shp\")\n",
    "\n",
    "# Only select district heating areas\n",
    "df_dh = df_dh[df_dh['vaerdi1203'] == 'Fjernvarme']\n",
    "\n",
    "# Convert to a different CRS\n",
    "df_dh = df_dh.to_crs(epsg=4326)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "1d4196a3-359e-4169-9eb4-f86335ce6c13",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "<br>\n",
    "\n",
    "## Nation wide"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 3,
   "id": "04574e1f-136f-41c7-903c-b8dbe8f31c84",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "image/png": "\n",
      "text/plain": [
       "<Figure size 576x576 with 1 Axes>"
      ]
     },
     "metadata": {
      "needs_background": "light"
     },
     "output_type": "display_data"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "plt.figure(figsize=(8, 8))\n",
    "\n",
    "proj = ccrs.PlateCarree()\n",
    "ax = plt.axes(projection=proj)\n",
    "\n",
    "ax.add_feature(cfeature.COASTLINE, lw=0.2)\n",
    "ax.add_feature(cfeature.LAND, alpha=0.6, facecolor='lightgrey')\n",
    "ax.add_feature(cfeature.BORDERS, alpha=0.6, edgecolor='black')\n",
    "\n",
    "df_dh['geometry'].plot(ax=ax, facecolor='r')\n",
    "ax.set_extent([7.8, 13, 54.5, 58])"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "0ff22495-42e2-40fd-a52b-0aa6a7720a41",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "<br>\n",
    "\n",
    "## Copenhagen district heating area\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 7,
   "id": "99c6eb3a-1454-42fe-980f-a7416c50a1d4",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "image/png": "\n",
      "text/plain": [
       "<Figure size 576x576 with 1 Axes>"
      ]
     },
     "metadata": {
      "needs_background": "light"
     },
     "output_type": "display_data"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "ctr_kommuner = ['Gentofte kommune', 'Gladsaxe kommune', 'Københavns kommune', 'Frederiksberg kommune', 'Tårnby kommune']\n",
    "veks_kommuner = ['Glostrup kommune', 'Roskilde kommune', 'Høje-Taastrup kommune', 'Albertslund kommune', 'Brøndby kommune', 'Hvidovre kommune',\n",
    "                 'Køge kommune', 'Solrød kommune', 'Greve kommune', 'Ishøj kommune', 'Vallensbæk kommune', 'Rødovre kommune']\n",
    "\n",
    "df_dh_ctr = df_dh[df_dh['cvrname'].isin(ctr_kommuner)]\n",
    "df_dh_veks = df_dh[df_dh['cvrname'].isin(veks_kommuner)]\n",
    "df_dh_vest = df_dh[df_dh['forsytekst'] == 'I/S Vestforbrændingen']\n",
    "\n",
    "plt.figure(figsize=(8, 8))\n",
    "\n",
    "proj = ccrs.PlateCarree()\n",
    "ax = plt.axes(projection=proj)\n",
    "ax.patch.set_facecolor('lightblue')\n",
    "ax.patch.set_alpha(0.05)\n",
    "\n",
    "token = os.environ.get('DAGI_DAF_WMS')\n",
    "\n",
    "ax.add_wms(wms=f\"https://api.dataforsyningen.dk/dagi_DAF?service=WMS&request=GetCapabilities&token={token}\",\n",
    "               layers=['Danmark'], zorder=0, alpha=0.8)\n",
    "\n",
    "params = {'lw': 0.4, 'edgecolor': 'k'}\n",
    "df_dh_ctr['geometry'].plot(ax=ax, color='orange', **params, label='CTR')\n",
    "df_dh_vest['geometry'].plot(ax=ax, color='green', **params, label='Vestforbrænding')\n",
    "df_dh_veks['geometry'].plot(ax=ax, color='lightblue', **params, label='VEKS')\n",
    "ax.set_extent([11.9, 12.8, 55.38, 55.8])\n",
    "\n",
    "handles = [mpatches.Patch(color='orange', label='CTR'),\n",
    "           mpatches.Patch(color='green', label='Vestforbrænding'),\n",
    "           mpatches.Patch(color='lightblue', label='VEKS')]\n",
    "ax.legend(handles=handles, loc='lower right', frameon=False, title='District heating supplier')\n",
    "plt.show()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "abf7822f-d8ad-4630-a53d-76c63f0860e7",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "Note the map is not completly perfect. In particular, there are some disconnected district heating areas denoted as VEKS that are in fact separate areas."
   ]
  },
